Synquizitive
Privacy Policy
Introduction
This Privacy Policy describes how Synquizitive ("we", "our", or "us") collects, uses, and shares your information when you use our mobile application.
Information We Collect
Personal Information
Player Name: We collect and store the display name you choose for multiplayer games
Device Information: Anonymous device identifiers for game session management
Game Data: Room codes, game scores, and gameplay statistics
Purchase History: Information about your in-app purchases and subscription status
Technical Data
Network connectivity status
App usage statistics and crash reports via Firebase Analytics
Game session data
Performance monitoring data
Advertising identifiers for personalized ads
Subscription and purchase data
How We Use Your Information
Essential Game Functions
Managing multiplayer game sessions
Maintaining game room states
Implementing real-time player presence
Facilitating player matchmaking
Processing and validating in-app purchases
Managing subscription status
Analytics and Improvements
Analyzing app performance
Identifying and fixing technical issues
Improving game features and user experience
Crash reporting and diagnostics
Understanding user engagement with advertisements
Optimizing subscription offerings
Data Storage and Security
Firebase Services
Firebase Realtime Database for game data storage
Firebase Authentication for anonymous user sessions
Firebase Analytics for app performance and usage statistics
Data is stored securely on Google Cloud Platform
RevenueCat
Secure storage of purchase and subscription data
Transaction history
Subscription status management
Data Retention
Game session data is temporarily stored during active games
Inactive game rooms are automatically deleted
Player names are stored locally on your device
Analytics data is retained according to Firebase's data retention policies
Purchase history is retained according to legal requirements
Subscription data is maintained while your account is active
Third Party Services
Firebase (Google)
Analytics and crash reporting
Real-time database functionality
Authentication services
Google AdSense
Delivers personalized advertisements
Collects ad interaction data
Uses device identifiers for ad targeting
May use cookies and similar technologies
RevenueCat
Processes and validates in-app purchases
Manages subscription lifecycles
Stores purchase history and subscription status
For more information about how these services process data, please visit:
Firebase
Google AdSense
RevenueCat
Advertising
We partner with Google AdSense to show advertisements in our app. This service may:
Use device identifiers and cookies for ad personalization
Collect data about ad interactions
Share data with Google's advertising partners
Use your interaction data to improve ad relevance
You can opt out of personalized advertising through your device settings.
In-App Purchases and Subscriptions
We use RevenueCat to manage in-app purchases and subscriptions. This service:
Processes payment information
Validates and maintains subscription status
Stores purchase history
Ensures secure transaction processing
Payment information is processed securely through your device's app store and is not directly accessible to us.
Your Rights and Choices
You can choose any display name
Game data can be cleared by uninstalling the app
Local data is removed when you uninstall the application
You can opt out of personalized advertising through your device settings
You can manage your subscription through your device's app store settings
Changes to This Policy
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy in the app.
Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at
